### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/todos

### Create task - VALID (on time expected)
POST http://localhost:8080/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Learn Spring Boot",
  "description": "Complete Phase A",
  "tentativeEndDate": "2026-07-20"
}

### Create task - MISSING NAME (400)
POST http://localhost:8080/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "Should fail",
  "tentativeEndDate": "2026-07-20"
}

### Create task - MISSING TENTATIVE DATE (400)
POST http://localhost:8080/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No tentative date",
  "description": "Should fail"
}

### Get task by valid ID
GET http://localhost:8080/todos/1

### Get task by invalid ID (404)
GET http://localhost:8080/todos/999

### Update task - VALID
PUT http://localhost:8080/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated task",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "tentativeEndDate": "2026-07-25",
  "actualEndDate": "2026-07-25"
}

### Update task - NOT FOUND (404)
PUT http://localhost:8080/todos/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Update nonexistent",
  "tentativeEndDate": "2026-07-20"
}

### Delete task by ID (204)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/todos/1

### Delete all tasks (204)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/todos